policies.content: You can cancel free of charge until 14 days before arrival. You'll be charged the total price of the reservation if you cancel in the 14 days before arrival. If you don’t show up you will be charged the total price of the reservation.

Children older than 1 year are welcome. 4 children from 1 to 6 year stay free of charge when using existing beds.
4 children from 6 to 11 year are charged  VND 100000 per night when using existing beds.
Up to two children from 1 to 7 year stay free of charge for extra beds.
The maximum number of extra beds in a room is 2.
The maximum number of total guests in a room is 15.
There is no capacity for cribs in the room.
Any type of extra bed is upon request and needs to be confirmed by management.
Additional fees are not calculated automatically in the total cost and will have to be paid for separately during your stay.
WiFi is available in public areas and is free of charge.
Free public parking is available  at a location nearby (reservation is not needed).
Pets are allowed on request. No extra charges.
You'll be charged a prepayment of the total price at any time.
The property reserves the right to pre-authorize credit cards prior to arrival.
